                    <h2 id="transfers-heading" class="h4">12. International Transfers</h2>
                    <p>Where data is transferred across borders, we use appropriate safeguards such as contractual clauses to protect your information.</p>
                </section>

                <section id="changes" class="mb-4" aria-labelledby="changes-heading">
